  "detailed_description": "In the future, America is a contaminated wasteland with more<br />\r\nthan 500 million people living in dence, populated cities.<br />\r\nPolitical scandals, high crime rate and slums.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA soldier in an unjust World, against swat and agents.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nABOUT GAMEPLAY:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Maps can only be played in order, one after the other.<br />\r\n-After killing enemy you will get Credits.<br />\r\n-You have unlimited ammunition, but every shot cost GAME CURRENCY (Credits).<br />\r\n-Player has two weapon slots. <br />\r\n-You can not change weapon slot 1 after collect the first weapon, only the second slot can be changed.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHINT:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYOU CAN SET UP YOUR OWN PERSONAL INPUTS UNDER OPTION",
